1-  displays latest version + json-server documentation: https://www.npmjs.com/package/json-server
2-  add following line to your package.json -> dependency:
      "dependencies": {
          "json-server": "^0.17.1"
      }
3-  The common way to start the json-server doesnt work.
    type "npx" before the command:
        - npx json-server --watch ./data/db.json
